rry (a05). So we'd try to swap carry (a05) with c01: doSwap(a05, c01). \n\nAfter doSwap: OR gate at bit 1 goes back to outputting c01, AND gate at bit 5 goes back to outputting a05. The carry chain is restored.\n\nThis would work. Let me add a test for this:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":192,"cache_read_input_tokens":82581,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":192},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d7889444-d33e-4b01-a64b-06d6ebe19ed8","uuid":"4274a7da-6ad8-49dc-8c1e-734b6a17e340"}
